room_title: Escape room "Abducted" by Escape Game Erie in Erie
review: This was the most fun we have had on a date! The abducted room was fun and challenging and I cannot wait to go back again!

room_title: Escape room "Abducted" by Escape Game Erie in Erie
review: We did 'Abducted'. It was so much fun. Definitely challenging, and you have to work with your teammates to make it out in time. My husband and I escaped with 1:55 left on the clock. We will for sure be coming back to get out of the other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Abducted" by Escape Game Erie in Erie
review: I loved it.  We had so much fun I brought my entire staff back as a team building experience.  If you haven't done it yet, you're in for a real treat.
